General Kibochi cautioned against laxity in following the Covid-19 safety protocols, especially with the country fighting the third wave of the pandemic. 

Additional reporting by Faith Nyamai and Steve Otieno Indian government has been supplying developing countries with free vaccine doses. Danish health officials said some patients developed blood clots since receiving the jab. The President has also announced that funerals will take place within 72 hours. In just 12 months, the number of the dead has swelled – now heading towards 1,900 in Kenya. There was presidential level security in Nairobi Hospital’s VIP North Wing and access to the premier hospital’s presidential suites was more severe than usual.